{"h82d8b246g1ce5g4d9bga8c3g1398540e0127": ["More drow. Fist - at the ready!", "c49b27b2-bd55-4c3f-a09a-7d787ab547ae", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "0912d009-b033-7552-2543-0ab8418cdb4c"], "h97a23a53g27bcg4191gaedbg16017c717717": ["I am no monster - I mean no harm to you. Tell me what happened here.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "150d45c2-1577-4b3d-823f-b85db2f8c7de"], "h0cb23c4cg95e4g4662gb0b2g712def68d0c0": ["Think carefully, <i>colnbluth. </i>Do you truly wish to anger Lolth's favoured?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "1def35f1-5a8e-0462-c535-8980abbb88d6"], "he0565bb0ga4bdg4138gac13g5956d45c8697": ["Save your breath.", "c49b27b2-bd55-4c3f-a09a-7d787ab547ae", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "a8865ef6-3ae0-1edc-7f37-b3e1aefa0613"], "h0eaa9855g81c8g4a98gaf1fgc42f705bdde6": ["No. We've suffered enough losses.", "c49b27b2-bd55-4c3f-a09a-7d787ab547ae", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "12afa9a6-6425-d93a-4559-f8c6603e7bf3"], "he87066d8ge59fg4e00gab3ag814e5837c4ab": ["Now please, just... leave me be.", "c49b27b2-bd55-4c3f-a09a-7d787ab547ae", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "5d1110e0-368c-c60b-0ddb-70cf52d75757"], "h8f479108gf15dg4666gb0f4g9b4074b664fa": ["Now please, just... leave me be. Speak to the Gauntlet if you want to know more.", "c49b27b2-bd55-4c3f-a09a-7d787ab547ae", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "d91fd4b4-444c-bb0e-814b-61694fb67143"], "h6cbb61a5g0bfeg41b5gbba4g4ac8f2dc7355": ["Be at ease. I didn't come seeking battle.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "a41ce58c-0564-5fa5-09b9-d8afd047aaee"], "h8b0d98b6g993ag4c9agabe5g80034862572b": ["You're... you're different than the others. I can tell.", "c49b27b2-bd55-4c3f-a09a-7d787ab547ae", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "15b4720f-42ac-5239-bd7e-0869b0825258"], "h9e7022b6g2d24g4cbdgbc9fg60628b2c1f64": ["It was a massacre. Drow and goblins slaughtered the lot. My poor Jacek never stood a chance.", "c49b27b2-bd55-4c3f-a09a-7d787ab547ae", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "8387ce96-9eca-f6cc-9f84-be7d54782710"], "h20a95db5ge333g4132gb47cg8f446ca97e63": ["He should never have been here in the first place. I'm the one that talked him into joining the Fist.", "c49b27b2-bd55-4c3f-a09a-7d787ab547ae", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "16dfda18-b0a4-572f-c2e5-a571d7058312"], "h76e48547g91ddg4623g8d3eg0b4bfcf57554": ["That's all I know. Please, just... leave me be. ", "c49b27b2-bd55-4c3f-a09a-7d787ab547ae", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "a203689f-47ad-4067-41fc-780945787f5a"], "hcc0ae505g21e7g48e8g921fgdedb8c269fe2": ["<i>Cast Detect Thoughts.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "76e20636-e371-49eb-aea3-3c7d9704a595"], "hf8c32db1g55ceg489bg8484g80921f3d01dc": ["<i>Another Lolth-sworn - a killmonger, a monster. If I do not take her head, she will take mine.</i>", "c49b27b2-bd55-4c3f-a09a-7d787ab547ae", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "61c3676e-a841-4f36-98c5-9ae9c1523ba5"], "h030e4fe2g37aeg4913g94a9ged99c9860826": ["What are you... you'll pay for that!", "c49b27b2-bd55-4c3f-a09a-7d787ab547ae", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "f1c84e1e-a8cc-4ccb-a2f4-1e471be9ecee"], "h7454f7ebg2c8fg4c4egad2dg24d2804a9237": ["<i>Attack.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "93ba563b-2e80-a5bf-f0d1-6cc84803a38a"], "h20a74e5eg0b6cg4857g897dg825eea47b349": ["More drow. Fist - at the ready!", "c49b27b2-bd55-4c3f-a09a-7d787ab547ae", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "e7eeca99-da92-067b-f7e0-ff93257e3252"], "h32a9d09dg7923g4d62gbe62ga70b847c5df1": ["Just <i>go.</i>", "c49b27b2-bd55-4c3f-a09a-7d787ab547ae", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "cff0f8d3-2138-bb9d-2020-8df0f0dd3212"], "h6adfb399gb4f0g4e14gb701gb19a7e9d5984": ["He Of The Unsleeping Eyes. Grant me the might to carry this burden. Grant me the faith to face darkness without fear.", "c49b27b2-bd55-4c3f-a09a-7d787ab547ae", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "0fdc08d3-96ae-9e01-2189-2bbe16558b10"], "h8ee53dc0gb9bfg47c5g8d43g0c75ec627385": ["What the hells happened here?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "ec2393f3-cbbc-b01c-c049-c0843318f37d"], "hf2996e2bg0768g46f4g84d8ga001738a70ed": ["A massacre. Drow and goblins slaughtered the lot.", "c49b27b2-bd55-4c3f-a09a-7d787ab547ae", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "cd6c451e-44eb-c5ca-f68f-5596e3751ff1"], "hc5155e9dg1f77g4642ga083gd543c279751c": ["Please. Just leave me be.", "c49b27b2-bd55-4c3f-a09a-7d787ab547ae", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "4d55b146-c57f-3851-a848-eb5842c191c0"], "h8bb15460g955fg4011gbaa8gf78ddc5a19ed": ["My condolences to you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "5f04fe38-7741-455f-2275-8b6becea9610"], "h64559a2dg3a3fg4c42ga944gf56ebf48dfc2": ["Looks like he wasn't cut out to be a Flaming Fist.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "eabee69b-ebfc-2c2a-b97b-ded77f4f2538"], "h7f5b2bc4g302bg43e7ga6bagcca59ec51e64": ["Only a coward would speak ill of the fallen.", "c49b27b2-bd55-4c3f-a09a-7d787ab547ae", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "8f33f804-f766-a5fd-fbba-432623ed1dc1"], "h3b16c84bg4628g45b4g8548g51a9d9c995eb": ["Would that the arrow had pierced <i>your</i> heart instead.", "c49b27b2-bd55-4c3f-a09a-7d787ab547ae", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "42f01619-747c-0a73-00f9-04dd9cf9a9a1"], "hfd4cece8g0871g47d7gabc0g92500971aab1": ["<i>Whisper a sympathetic prayer.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "cdfe7173-f697-828b-e200-afe0be08bb92"], "h9222a8c5g2c18g46fdg8f2ag3e63b9c7b9c3": ["Steel our blades and temper our hearts for the battles in this life and next.", "c49b27b2-bd55-4c3f-a09a-7d787ab547ae", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "f7e994a4-4268-a1fa-390c-290aec506478"], "h024fc1d5g66cbg4abbg95d7gb43926021cd2": ["May I ask what happened here?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "635fcc48-e44d-d1c5-26c2-3f3c57b7cce6"], "hcf3a5975g33f1g4a82g908eged0f74167630": ["He is at rest now.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "fe062096-a35e-3b49-0354-823419df49ca"], "h7c967d1bg764cg4c12g8f0cg1ff36f1d84be": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "20fcb30d-85db-972c-8729-74dcd3085fe2"], "h08f05834g9a3eg425aga62fg8d3cc81d9c73": ["<i>Join the woman in prayer: </i>'Steel our blades...'", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "4c6f513b-18ee-27c6-ebcd-87b257edc749"], "ha1f295e2gba26g424aga323gfb04cd07269a": ["... and temper our hearts for the battles in this life and next.", "c49b27b2-bd55-4c3f-a09a-7d787ab547ae", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "a193098f-7f07-281d-7eeb-6ea56bd22530"], "h340880bdg8f17g4466ga240g6ba2366f3d14": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "ee0a06bb-a35d-17ad-a423-bcf3386ba56a"], "h2000a510ge0d1g4102g8249gb2c63b6d41f3": ["I promise my shield and my sword, Vigilant One. Let them be my courage...", "c49b27b2-bd55-4c3f-a09a-7d787ab547ae", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "b5158f2d-0a0a-bb78-459c-e4cae3ed5635"], "h9af2244cg13d5g45d1g9619g5b46da8e83eb": ["Get back.", "c49b27b2-bd55-4c3f-a09a-7d787ab547ae", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "8ec1ab96-6a03-c368-61c8-874b43e7f400"], "hb725256fg7076g483fgba7eg946d40ac2a8c": ["Back, I say!", "c49b27b2-bd55-4c3f-a09a-7d787ab547ae", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "1a429f9b-8945-9411-34b8-312631d6111a"], "h083ec180g0e8eg479bg8f76g7b4be692d3bf": ["Away from me.", "c49b27b2-bd55-4c3f-a09a-7d787ab547ae", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "f481313e-f5d2-ecac-c241-cd4472618590"], "hd1de7983g340ag4279g9e24gd1b4ec241a44": ["What the hells happened here?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "84b20ace-65dd-ad46-0a1e-5e7f1d39767e"], "h931dc796gb8f2g41d0g8a8cg418710dad092": ["Speak to the Gauntlet. She'll tell you more.", "c49b27b2-bd55-4c3f-a09a-7d787ab547ae", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "4826041f-b556-3308-5720-b986054a138c"], "h79d1598cgdd97g4264gb430gb9e33861e94f": ["... the Fist Gauntlet included.", "c49b27b2-bd55-4c3f-a09a-7d787ab547ae", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "cabf96f8-64db-2ace-54c6-9be119e68b61"], "h3623ad58g5955g420ag85f2g46c0ada10228": ["You should know there are Zhentarim in the area.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "e79c3488-d310-2f27-b50b-f08709396caf"], "hdd5fe3b4g07a2g4206g928fg4c38df703a04": ["I'll note your concern. I'd do more, were we not so slight in number.", "c49b27b2-bd55-4c3f-a09a-7d787ab547ae", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "cbb1759c-ab2d-853f-ac95-1a0a19f77b34"], "hff232cacg1e7fg44c1gaf61g97c1c958b3ab": ["I just wanted to tell you there's a Zhentarim operation nearby.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "07ec46a0-615f-37da-35f2-952351360628"], "h7f8129f7g7d17g4c5dg8c6cg438fd21e4d43": ["Away, I tell you!", "c49b27b2-bd55-4c3f-a09a-7d787ab547ae", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_FlamingFist5.html", "63ba1b9f-867a-aace-af5c-47785b61a657"]}